title: Cafe Schneior
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Israeli, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Neighborhood cafe on side street near Bograshov. Many vegetarian and vegan items clearly marked. Offers breakfast and brunch, salads, sandwiches, pasta, and more. Meets the Israeli "vegan friendly" standard. No extra charge for soy milk in coffee.
